repos.description: Just a copy of https://classic.minecraft.net/ (or at least as much as I could). Included, will be some popular or fitting resource packs converted to work with this version.

repos.name: nes-template
repos.description: A template for a Nintendo Entertainment System project, using the ca65 assembler, targeting a UNROM (CHR-RAM + PRG bankswitching) board. Includes toolchain, and has build infrastructure for Windows and Linux.
